# GPU 与渲染规范

## L1 资源管理
- Buffer → `BufferPool.acquire/release`，禁止手动 `destroy()`
- Texture → `TextureManager.create/release`
- 每个资源必须 `GPUMemoryTracker.track()`
- 小 Uniform → `GPUUploader.writeUniform()`（走 `queue.writeBuffer`）
- 大数据 → `BufferPool.acquireStaging()`（StagingRing 4MB×3 三重缓冲）
- Worker Transferable → `GPUUploader.uploadFromTransferable()`
- 禁止 L2~L6 直接调用 `device.createBuffer/createTexture`

## DeviceManager GPU 驱动差异
- `DeviceManager.needsWorkaround(id)` 检查特定 GPU 问题
- 已知 workaround：`intel-arc-jitter`（浮点抖动）/ `mobile-depth-precision`（深度精度）/ `safari-texture-limit`（纹理尺寸）
- vendorId 基于 `GPUAdapterInfo` 推断

## TextureManager DynamicAtlas
- `addToAtlas(atlasId, imageData, padding?)` → 运行时打包小纹理到大 Atlas
- 内置 Atlas ID：`"icons"`（精灵图）/ `"glyphs"`（MSDF 字形）/ `"patterns"`（填充图案）
- 填充图案（#10.2）：通过 Atlas + 视口/世界空间 UV 选择保持缩放一致密度

## SurfaceConfig
```typescript
interface SurfaceConfig {
  canvas: HTMLCanvasElement;
  devicePixelRatio: number;
  width: number; height: number;           // CSS
  physicalWidth: number; physicalHeight: number; // 物理
  format: GPUTextureFormat;
  alphaMode: GPUCanvasAlphaMode;
  sampleCount: 1 | 4;                     // MSAA
}
```

## 深度缓冲
- 始终 Reversed-Z：近→1.0 远→0.0
- `depthCompare: 'greater'`，clear `0.0`
- 格式：`depth32float`
- 3D：对数深度 + `perspectiveReversedZInfinite`
- 2D：正交 + Reversed-Z

## FrameGraphBuilder
```typescript
interface FrameGraphBuilder {
  begin(surface, camera): void;
  addFrustumCullPass(options): string;
  addDepthSortPass(options): string;
  addLabelCollisionPass(options): string;
  addSceneRenderPass({ id, projection, layers: Layer[], clearColor?, dependencies? }): string;
  addPostProcessPass({ id, factory, inputPassId }): string;
  addScreenPass({ layers }): string;
  addPickingPass({ layers, pixelX?, pixelY? }): string;
  build(): CompiledRenderGraph;
}
```

## PickingEngine
- Color-ID 像素级 picking
- `pickAt(x, y)` → `Promise<PickResult | null>`（异步，延迟 1 帧）
- `readDepthAt(x, y)` → 深度值
- `unprojectScreenToWorld()` → 3D 世界坐标
- `screenToGeodetic()` → 射线与椭球体求交

## Compute Pass 内置任务
- frustum-cull：视锥剔除
- depth-sort：GPU Parallel Radix Sort
- label-collision：标注碰撞精筛
- point-cluster：GPU 空间哈希聚合
- terrain-tessellation：地形细分

## Pipeline 缓存
- `getOrCreateAsync()` 异步编译不阻塞
- `warmup()` 预热常用 Pipeline
- 首次使用某材质前必须预编译

## EngineConfig
```typescript
interface EngineConfig {
  devicePixelRatio: number | 'auto';
  maxPixelRatio: number;       // 默认 2
  sampleCount: 1 | 4;
  gpuMemoryBudget: number;     // 默认 512MB
  cpuMemoryBudget: number;     // 默认 1GB
  tileCacheSize: number;       // 默认 512
  workerCount: number | 'auto';
  maxConcurrentRequests: number; // 默认 6
  useLogarithmicDepth: boolean;
  useReversedZ: boolean;
  requestRenderMode: boolean;
  targetFrameRate: number;     // 默认 60
  backgroundThrottleMs: number; // 默认 1000
  logLevel: 'debug'|'info'|'warn'|'error'|'none';
}
```
